tool_input:
{"arg": "Run query to check HDFS disk space utilization:
```sql
SELECT dfs_used, dfs_remaining, dfs_capacity FROM dfs_space;
```
Also, check disk space utilization on the TaskTrackers. Specifically check disk usage in /mnt/hadoop/tmp and /mnt/hadoop/mapred/local directories."}

{"arg": "Run query to check HDFS disk space utilization:
```sql
SELECT dfs_used, dfs_remaining, dfs_capacity FROM dfs_space;
```
Also, check disk space utilization on the TaskTrackers. Specifically check disk usage in /mnt/hadoop/tmp and /mnt/hadoop/mapred/local directories."}

{"arg": "Run query to get average size of records before and after upgrade:
```sql
SELECT avg(LENGTH(CONCAT(timestamp, user_id, url, http_status_code, bytes_sent, user_agent, ip_address, country_code, session_id))) as avg_size_before FROM weblogs WHERE timestamp < '2024-11-10';
SELECT avg(LENGTH(CONCAT(timestamp, user_id, url, http_status_code, bytes_sent, user_agent, ip_address, country_code, session_id, device_type))) as avg_size_after FROM weblogs WHERE timestamp >= '2024-11-10';
```"}

{"arg": "Run query to get average size of records before and after upgrade:
```sql
SELECT avg(LENGTH(CONCAT(timestamp, user_id, url, http_status_code, bytes_sent, user_agent, ip_address, country_code, session_id))) as avg_size_before FROM weblogs WHERE timestamp < '2024-11-10';
SELECT avg(LENGTH(CONCAT(timestamp, user_id, url, http_status_code, bytes_sent, user_agent, ip_address, country_code, session_id, device_type))) as avg_size_after FROM weblogs WHERE timestamp >= '2024-11-10';
```"}

completion:
Based on the incident report and the available specialist agents, the appropriate delegation of debugging tasks would be as follows:

{
  "Log Analyzer": {
    "task": "Analyze the sales transaction logs to identify any errors or anomalies that may have led to the missing data",
    "instruction": "Investigate the logs for any errors, exceptions, or unexpected behavior that could have caused the data loss during the holiday season."
  },
  "Schema Checker": {
    "task": "Validate the data schema of the sales transaction data and identify any schema violations",
    "instruction": "Examine the data schema to ensure that it is correctly structured and that there are no schema-level issues that could have contributed to the missing data."
  },
  "Fix Proposer": {
    "task": "Propose potential fixes to address the missing data issue in the sales transaction data",
    "instruction": "Based on the findings from the Log Analyzer and Schema Checker, provide recommendations for fixes or improvements to the data pipeline to prevent similar issues in the future."
  }
}

